      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
        Built with <span class="text-red-400">♥</span> using <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">Astro</a> + <a href="https://threejs.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">Three.js</a>
